# Noein Solutions — Landing Page

Marketing / brochure site for **Noein Solutions** (digital delivery consulting for AEC) and its SaaS product **Capsar.io**. Principal: Andrea Aita. Production domain: `noeinsolutions.com`.

## Tech Stack

- **Plain HTML5** multi-page static site (no framework, no build step, no bundler)
- **Single CSS file** (`css/styles.css`, ~2400 lines) with CSS custom properties
- **Single JS file** (`js/main.js`) — vanilla ES5-style IIFE, no modules/imports
- **Google Fonts**: DM Sans (body), Instrument Serif (display headings)
- **No package.json** — zero npm dependencies
- **Deploy**: bash `deploy.sh` via rsync/scp to Docker nginx on Hetzner

