## Conventions

- **No build pipeline** — edit HTML/CSS/JS directly; changes go live via `deploy.sh`
- **Duplicated page shell** — nav and footer are copy-pasted across all `.html` files (no includes/partials). When editing nav or footer, update every page.
- **BEM-ish class naming** — compound names like `.hero-inner--centered`, `.contact-tab--active`
- **Section rhythm** — `.section-label` → `.section-title` → `.section-sub` → content
- **Fade-in pattern** — add `.fade-in` to any section; `IntersectionObserver` in `main.js` adds `.visible`
- **Buttons** — `.btn .btn-primary` (gold filled) or `.btn .btn-outline` (bordered)
- **Typography** — use HTML entities for special chars (`&mdash;`, `&rsquo;`, `&pound;`)
- **Icons** — inline SVGs, no icon library
- **Accessibility** — `aria-label`/`aria-expanded` on interactive elements; focus styles in CSS

## Coding Standards

- Keep JS as vanilla ES5 (no `const`/`let`/arrow functions/`class`) — the current codebase uses `var` and `function` throughout
- CSS goes in `css/styles.css` — group new rules under the relevant comment banner section
- Prefer CSS custom properties over hardcoded values
- External links: `target="_blank" rel="noopener"`
- Images: use `loading="lazy"` for below-fold images
- Forms: include `aria-required="true"` on required fields

## External Services

- **FormSubmit.co** — contact form POST endpoint (honeypot `_honey` field)
- **Calendly** — embedded booking widget on contact page
- **Capsar.io app** — `https://app.noeinsolutions.com`

## Deploy

`deploy.sh` rsyncs to `root@77.42.70.26:/var/www/noeinsol`, excludes `.git`, `.cursor`, `*.plan.md`, deploy/nginx configs, then reloads Docker nginx. Run with `--dry-run` to preview.
